      • handleUnloadRequest

        public void handleUnloadRequest(PulsarService pulsar,
                                long timeout,
                                TimeUnit timeoutUnit)
                         throws Exception
        It unloads the bundle by closing all topics concurrently under this bundle. 
         a. disable bundle ownership in memory and not in zk
 b. close all the topics concurrently
 c. delete ownership znode from zookeeper.
        参数:
        pulsar -
        timeout - timeout for unloading bundle. It doesn't throw exception if it timesout while waiting on closing all topics
        timeoutUnit -
        抛出:
        Exception
